query:
UPDATE island_guides SET 
atoll = CASE slug
  WHEN 'thulusdhoo-island' THEN 'Kaafu Atoll'
  WHEN 'kandooma-island' THEN 'South Malé Atoll'
  WHEN 'dhigurah-island' THEN 'Alif Dhaal Atoll'
  WHEN 'rasdhoo-island' THEN 'Alif Alif Atoll'
  WHEN 'veligandu-island' THEN 'Alif Alif Atoll'
  WHEN 'maafushi-island' THEN 'Kaafu Atoll'
  WHEN 'fulidhoo-island' THEN 'Vaavu Atoll'
  WHEN 'felidhoo-island' THEN 'Vaavu Atoll'
  ELSE atoll
END,
flightInfo = CASE slug
  WHEN 'thulusdhoo-island' THEN 'By Flight: 30 minutes domestic flight from Male to Kaafu Atoll'
  WHEN 'kandooma-island' THEN 'By Flight: 30 minutes domestic flight from Male to South Malé Atoll'
  WHEN 'dhigurah-island' THEN 'By Flight: 45 minutes domestic flight from Male to Alif Dhaal Atoll'
  WHEN 'rasdhoo-island' THEN 'By Flight: 40 minutes domestic flight from Male to Alif Alif Atoll'
  WHEN 'veligandu-island' THEN 'By Flight: 40 minutes domestic flight from Male to Alif Alif Atoll'
  WHEN 'maafushi-island' THEN 'By Flight: 30 minutes domestic flight from Male to Kaafu Atoll'
  WHEN 'fulidhoo-island' THEN 'By Flight: 50 minutes domestic flight from Male to Vaavu Atoll'
  WHEN 'felidhoo-island' THEN 'By Flight: 50 minutes domestic flight from Male to Vaavu Atoll'
  ELSE flightInfo
END
WHERE slug IN ('thulusdhoo-island', 'kandooma-island', 'dhigurah-island', 'rasdhoo-island', 'veligandu-island', 'maafushi-island', 'fulidhoo-island', 'felidhoo-island');
